    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and kept in a garage, so the finish is still sparkling. It drives like a beauty and has been super reliable. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3. This specimen features the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe, rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells, and a complete Besian VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing deflection, and the exterior finish exhibits exceptional depth with no clear coat failure or oxidation. A mechanically pure example for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. Original paint with no scratches. Interior is flawless. Full service history available. Runs perfectly.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
