    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in showroom condition. The exterior paint is finished in a deep gloss with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, having been protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating and kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. The factory alloy wheels are flawless, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-total tread life remaining. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or bolster wear, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Every technological feature\u2014from the navigation interface to the premium surround-sound system\u2014operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule by certified master technicians. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a buyer who demands perfection and a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
